thread.title: BRIEF- Beijing SuperMap Software sees 2017 net profit up 40.5 pct to 64.8 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF- Beijing SuperMap Software sees 2017 net profit up 40.5 pct to 64.8 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - beijing supermap software co ltd

text:
Jan 23(Reuters) - Beijing SuperMap Software Co Ltd
* Sees 2017 net profit to increase by 40.5 percent to 64.8 percent, or to be 179 million yuan to 210 million yuan
* Says 2016 net profit was 127.5 million yuan
* Says that enlarged scale of main business and inclusion of new company as main reasons for the forecast
